text: Anajaira Maciel Claudio Burgos (born 24 August 1996) is a Dominican former footballer who played as a forward. She has been a member of the Dominican Republic women's national team. ==International career== Claudio capped for the Dominican Republic at senior level during the 2012 CONCACAF Women's Olympic Qualifying Tournament. == References == Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Dominican Republic women's footballers Category:Dominican Republic women's international footballers
